      "author": "zhouzeqiang",
      "description": "### 主要增加功能：\r\n增加支持Excel文件在Obsidian中打开，可以进行简单快速浏览Excel。\r\n\r\n### 其他功能：\r\n1、在文件显示区域实现tab标签页功能：打开docx、Excel、ppt等文件时，每个文件新建一个tab，打开前先判断是否已经打开，已打开则激活现有tab而非新建窗口\r\n2、修复i18n翻译缺失导致界面显示原始key的问题\r\n3、修复引用列表显示不存在文件的问题\r\n4、更换拖动区域和Excel列调整的图标为ChevronsUpDown\r\n5、更换Obsidian工具栏图标为notebook-text\r\n\r\n---\r\n### Main added features:\r\nAdd support for opening Excel files in Obsidian, allowing for simple and quick browsing of Excel.\r\n\r\n### Other functions:\r\n1. Implement tabbed page functionality in the file display area: When opening files such as docx, Excel, and ppt, create a new tab for each file. Before opening, check whether it has already been opened. If it has, activate the existing tab instead of creating a new window\r\n2. Fix the issue where the original key is displayed on the interface due to missing i18n translation\r\n3. Fix the issue where the reference list displays files that do not exist\r\n4. Replace the icons for dragging areas and Excel column resizing with ChevronsUpDown\r\n5. Replace the Obsidian toolbar icon with a notebook-text icon",
